ng NS-BH systems would weaken the\nprospects for electromagnetic detection. However, EM observations, including\nnon-detections, can significantly tighten the constraints on spin and mass\nratio.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Aug 2021 13:59:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 7 Jan 2022 10:07:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-19"}
