 expansions,\nasset growth or acquisitions which may require heavy funding. In this way,\nfirms will be assured of improved performance as well as high financial growth.\nThe study also recommends for substantial firm financing through equity. Value:\nEquity financing is important to any firm, if the proceeds are used to invest\nin projects which eventually bring growth to the firm.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Aug 2021 15:34:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-24"}
